  "ID": "200701-19",
  "Title": "OpenLDAP: Insecure usage of /tmp during installation",
  "Synopsis": "\n    A shell script commonly released with OpenLDAP makes insecure usage of\n    files in /tmp during the emerge process.\n  ",
